Saturday for more intensive efforts to prevent haze, which has
affected most ASEAN countries over the past two months, from
getting worse. (Malaysia-ASEAN-Haze)
</P>
<P>
- - - -
</P>
<P>
BANGKOK -- Thailand's new constitution has come into force
Saturday after King Bhumibol Adulyadej signed it, written on a
traditional scroll.
</P>
<P>
