Meanwhile, Angolan Foreign Minister Venancio de Moura, when
meeting China's Ambassador Xiao Sijin on October 9, reiterated
that his government will stick to the "one China" policy, saying
that his government recognized the People's Republic of China as
the sole legal government of China, and Taiwan is only part of
China. 
