<HEADLINE> Police Detain Five England Soccer Fans </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ROME, October 10 (Xinhua) -- Five England fans were detained
here Friday night after trying to steal drink from a bar and
throwing bottles at Italian police.
</P>
<P>
The trouble started after England fans arrived at Rome's main
Termini station on Saturday night's World Cup qualifier with
Italy.
</P>
