<HEADLINE> China's First Composers Association </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HEFEI, October 11 (Xinhua) -- Renowned Chinese composers have
sent congratulatory messages on the establishment of the Anhui
Province Association of Composers, the first organization of its
kind in China.
</P>
<P>
Composers throughout the nation point to the establishment of
the organization as a great event for China's musical circle.
</P>
<P>
The over 100 members of the association will contribute to the
province's musical prosperity and help other composers create
excellent works for the people, according to officials.
</P>
<P>
The association plans to organize symposiums, hold concerts and
provide training for music lovers.  
</P>
