<HEADLINE> Market Exchange Rates </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, October 11 (Xinhua) -- The People's Bank of China today
issued the market exchange rates in RMB yuan against three major
currencies. The middle price of RMB against convertible
currencies is mainly based on the closing price of the preceding
interbank trading.
</P>
<P>
The designated foreign exchange trading banks will decide the
exchange rates in RMB yuan against other convertible currenies
according to the tone of the international exchagne market and the
rules of the People's Bank of China.
</P>
<P>
Market Exchange Rates (in RMB yuan)
</P>
<P>
Currency  Unit  Middle Price
</P>
<P>
US Dollar 100 828.35
</P>
<P>
Japanese Yen  100 6.8321
</P>
<P>
HK Dollar 100 107.05 
</P>
